# data artifacts — bronze JSONL is COMMITTED on purpose (repo-as-database
# mode: data/raw/*.jsonl is the accumulating fact store, compacted by
# content_hash). Only the local DuckDB build artifact + regenerable API
# caches (e.g. the 15 MB Sleeper player dict) stay out.
data/*.duckdb
data/cache/

